text: Only tried the noodle stall. Very plain and not much ingredient, not sure how this could be a franchise stall. Service attitude need to improve too, although they have all kinds of dried noodle can’t replace rice that comes with the soup, unlike other noodle stall eg. Yi Pan which is much more accommodating to customer’s need.
The canned drinks there are horribly expensive, the price increased to 1.90!!
